### 1. Admin: Create Product (Allowed)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "new-admin-product-{{$randomInt}}",
  "title": "Admin Created Product",
  "subtitle": "Subtitle",
  "brandName": "GAYAKINI",
  "description": "Description",
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

### 2. Admin: Create Product (Denied - Customer Role)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "denied-product",
  "title": "Should Fail",
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

### 3. Admin: Create Product (Denied - Anonymous)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "denied-product",
  "title": "Should Fail"
}

### 4. Admin: List Orders
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json
